OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer joins ITV News'
OL,7,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston for the
OL,8,FTalking Politics podcast, as the prime
OL,9,Fminister travels to the Gulf following
OL,10,Fthe US-Iran ceasefire
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,13,Ftold ITV News' Talking Politics
OL,14,Fpodcast that he is "fed up" with
OL,15,Ffamilies in the UK seeing their bills
OL,16,Fgo up and down "because of the actions
OL,17,Fof Putin or Trump".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
