CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FThe exclusive interview with ITV News'
OL,7,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston is the
OL,8,Fprime minister's first since the
OL,9,Festablishment of a fragile two-week
OL,10,Fceasefire deal made between the US and
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FBut the prime minister said that
OL,14,Fdespite the ceasefire, the impact of
OL,15,Fthe crisis in the Middle East on the
OL,16,FUK is "clear to see."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,F"I'm fed up with the fact that
OL,7,Ffamilies across the country see their
OL,8,Fbills go up and down on energy,
OL,9,Fbusinesses' bills go up and down on
OL,10,Fenergy, because of the actions of
OL,11,FPutin or Trump across the world," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FIn the interview, Starmer emphasised
OL,15,Fthe need for increased energy
OL,16,Fresilience and independence, warning
OL,17,Fthat people in the UK will be "paying
OL,18,Ffor the war."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FStarmer also addressed the "reopening"
OL,7,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, a vital
OL,8,Fwaterway which remained effectively
OL,9,Fclosed up until the deal was struck on
OL,10,FTuesday evening.
OL,12,FThe closure of the Strait has caused
OL,13,Fstock markets to plummet worldwide and
OL,14,Foil prices to sharply increase.
OL,16,FIran's deputy foreign minister told
OL,17,FITV News' International Editor Emma
OL,18,FMurphy earlier on Thursday that the
OL,19,FStrait "is open", but the prime
OL,20,Fminister said that needs to be
OL,21,F"tested".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,F"Our position is 'open means open' for
OL,7,Fsafe navigation. That means toll-free
OL,8,Fnavigation and vessels can get
OL,9,Fthrough."
OL,11,FHowever, Starmer said the world will
OL,12,Fhave to "wait and see" whether the
OL,13,FStrait's opening fully materialises.
OL,15,FReports have suggested that part of
OL,16,Fthe ceasefire agreement could be the
OL,17,Fright for Iran to impose tolls on
OL,18,Fships passing through the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,F"Some of the discussions in the last
OL,7,Fcouple of days have been, let's see
OL,8,Fwhat happens in two, three, four days.
OL,10,F"That'll begin to be the test. So it's
OL,11,Fnot what people say on day one or day
OL,12,Ftwo."
OL,14,FIsrael "should stop" strikes on Lebanon
OL,16,FIn the wide-ranging interview, Starmer
OL,17,Falso said Israel is "wrong" to
OL,18,Fcontinue its strikes on Lebanon amid a
OL,19,Fceasefire with Iran, saying it "should
OL,20,Fstop" as a "matter of principle".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FIsrael's continued strikes on Lebanon,
OL,7,Fdespite the ceasefire, have been a
OL,8,Fpoint of contention which have
OL,9,Fthreatened the stability of the
OL,10,Fceasefire.
OL,12,FLate Thursday, Israeli Prime Minister
OL,13,FBenjamin Netanyahu said his cabinet
OL,14,Fwill hold talks with Lebanon "as soon
OL,15,Fas possible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FWhen asked whether the strikes were a
OL,7,Fbreach of the ceasefire, the prime
OL,8,Fminister said: "It's hard to say that
OL,9,Fthere is a breach when we haven't all
OL,10,Fgot access to all the details of the
OL,11,Fceasefire.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer said that
OL,14,Fa cessation of strikes on Lebanon
OL,15,Fshould be part of the US-Iran
OL,16,Fceasefire agreement.
OL,18,F"But let me be really clear about it.
OL,19,FThey're wrong. That shouldn't be
OL,20,Fhappening. That should stop."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FStarmer added: "The question isn't a
OL,7,Ftechnical one of whether it's a breach
OL,8,Fof the agreement or not. The question
OL,9,Fis actually a matter of principles."
OL,11,FOn Trump's comments
OL,13,FThe ceasefire was forged as a result
OL,14,Fof a deadline US President Donald
OL,15,FTrump imposed on Iran to open the
OL,16,FStrait, or "a whole civilisation will
OL,17,Fdie."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FThe prime minister did not go as far
OL,7,Fas condemning the president's
OL,8,Flanguage, but said it was "not
OL,9,Flanguage I would use."
OL,11,F"I'm clear that for the United
OL,12,FKingdom, we have our principles, we
OL,13,Fhave our values, we will be guided by
OL,14,Fthem in everything that we do."
OL,16,FIt is these principles that the prime
OL,17,Fminister has echoed for his reasoning
OL,18,Fbehind not joining the war in Iran,
OL,19,Finstead only allowing the US to use
OL,20,FBritish air bases for defensive
OL,21,Factions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,F"I'm not going to waver or yield to
OL,7,Fany pressure": Keir Starmer says he
OL,8,Fwon't be pushed into the war despite
OL,9,Fthe criticism his decisions drew.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FUK will not be "dragged" in to war
OL,18,FThe Iranian deputy foreign minister,
OL,19,Fhowever, accused the UK of allowing
OL,20,Fthe US to launch B2 bombers for
OL,21,Foffensive strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FThe prime minister firmly disputed
OL,7,Fthis, saying "our bases will not be
OL,8,Fand are not being used for wider
OL,9,Foffensive and particularly for
OL,10,Foffensive on civilians".
OL,12,F"From the get-go, we've been
OL,13,Fmonitoring this situation. So I'm
OL,14,Fpretty clear in my own mind about what
OL,15,Fwe've agreed and what the use of the
OL,16,Fbases are."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,F"I've been saying we are not going to
OL,7,Fbe dragged into this war because I say
OL,8,Fthere must be a lawful basis. That
OL,9,Fmatters if you're going to commit our
OL,10,Fservice personnel to risk their lives."
OL,12,FThe prime minister will continue to
OL,13,Fmeet Gulf leaders on Thursday, after
OL,14,Falready having met Saudi Crown Prince
OL,15,FMohammed Bin Salman and UAE President
OL,16,FSheikh Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
