FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775837470
OL,3,CStarmer: 'I'm fed up' seeing bills go
OL,4,Cup and down because 'of Putin or Trump'
OL,6,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,7,FNetanyahu said he had ordered his
OL,8,Fcabinet to begin direct negotiations
OL,9,Fwith Lebanon. Talks between the two
OL,10,Fcountries are expected to be held next
OL,11,Fweek in Washington.
OL,13,FTalks between the US and Iran are due
OL,14,Fto take place in Pakistan this
OL,15,Fweekend, with Vance and envoy Steve
OL,16,FWitkoff to attend from the Trump
OL,17,Fadministration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
